Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Conan Episode 1010 "The \NIdol Whose Smile Disappeared"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,[OP]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,[ED]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,[Eyecatch]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:33.93,DCMain,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,A dine and dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A journey of a thousand miles \Nstarts with the first step!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.48,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Solve 1,000 mysteries and enter a new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.56,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A dine and dash in Beika City?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:43.53,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A popular idol is behaving mysteriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.02,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.90,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.56,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:37.01,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(401,1)}The Idol Whose Smile Disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"The Idol Whose Smile Disappeared!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.51,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\shad0\fs30\fnArial\blur2\c&H7E66D9&\3c&H5E372B&\pos(320,152)}Poirot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.90,sign_4177_14_Detective_Agency,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.34,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.17,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:23.70,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Starting today, I transferred from the Haido City \Npolice box to the Beika City police box on 4-chome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.93,Yamasato,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(441,1)}Yamasato Futoshi (28)\NPatrol Officer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.93,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My name is Yamasato Futoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Officer Yamasato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:32.56,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,There's a case I'd like you to \Ncrack, Detective Mori Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.93,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Crack a case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.19,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, crack a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.15,DCMain,YAMATO,0000,0000,0000,,Our story begins with a \Nsingle phone call I received
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.20,DCMain,YAMATO,0000,0000,0000,,at the Beika City 4-chome police box today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:46.70,Police Boxes,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(115,1)\pos(294,82)\frz12.3\fs23\c&H96B3C8&\3c&HD3E9F3&\shad1\4c&H9AB3BE&}Beika Police Station Beika 4-chome Police Box
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.70,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Beika City 4-chomeâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:50.20,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What? A dine and dash at a family restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.49,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.60,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I headed there immediately, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.97,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What? The dine and dash has been resolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:07.96,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds before I arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:13.00,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,the blonde girl who dine and dashed \Nreturned with her mother to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds before, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:17.10,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,We passed by each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:22.29,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,When I arrived at the restaurant, I encountered\Na sobbing blonde girl and her mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.24,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,who was supporting her, in \Nfront of the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:31.44,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,According to the mother, her daughter \Nforgot her wallet and panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:34.05,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So it's been solved, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have a drink to celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.93,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you. I'm currently on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.51,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, the case isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:46.94,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is what the waitstaff said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:50.43,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,They claim the girl who dine and dashed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:54.52,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,and the girl who came to apologize seemed \Nlike completely different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:05:00.02,DCItalic,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who dine and dashed was \Na blonde wearing sunglasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:07.03,DCItalic,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,but she seemed like a different person from the \Ngirl who just came to apologize with her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:09.25,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:13.33,DCItalic,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,When I brought the chocolate \Nparfait to her table,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.79,DCItalic,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,I got a glimpse of her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:21.59,DCItalic,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,The smile she had then looked just like hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.88,sign_7711_52_It_s_cold_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(250,157,250,320)}It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.88,sign_7711_53_Draft_Beer,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(483,157,483,315)}Draft Beer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.92,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Her? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:31.51,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Apparently her smile looked just \Nlike that of idol Kakurai Kayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:31.35,Kayoko,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(399,395)}Kakurai Kayoko (20)\NIdol
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:37.85,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... there was another similar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:43.86,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,It happened three months ago at the police box \Nin Haido City where I was stationed at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:48.36,Police Boxes,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(188,1)\pos(285,67)\frz12.62\frx10\fry0\fs23\3c&H262219&\4c&H262219&\c&H537C83&}Haido City Police Box #8
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.78,DCNote,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(444,443)\pos(327,273)\blur2\3c&H444B4A&\bord3}3 Months Earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.36,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Haido City 5-chome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.62,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What? A dine and dash at a ramen restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.23,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.50,sign_8500_65_Sasai_New_Haido_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(497,18)\fad(354,1)}New Haido Ramen\N{\fs26}Sasai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.68,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I headed there immediately, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.91,DCItalic,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What? The case has been resolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.81,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,According to the owner, as in \Ntoday's family restaurant case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:11.01,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,it was a blonde woman in \Nsunglasses who dine and dashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:16.52,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as she finished eating \Nher ramen, she suddenly ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.81,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,The owner immediately called it in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:26.02,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,but after ten minutes, the blonde and a \Nwoman claiming to be her older sister showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:32.26,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,According to the sister, her younger \Nsister forgot her wallet and panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.28,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Those are similar stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.78,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So, did the owner of the\Nramen restaurant also say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:44.28,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,that the blonde with sunglasses\Nlooked like Kakurai Kayoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.13,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:45.80,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:53.07,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That evening, at the Haido City Hall, \Nthere was a DDPP handshake event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.05,sign_9784_80_Handshake_Event_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\bord3}Handshake\NEvent\N\N\NEntrance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,DDPP?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:59.06,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,It's the idol group Kakurai \NKayoko belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.31,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko is the star of DDPP.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.82,sign_10185_84_Kakurai_Kayoko,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(237,1)\move(522,24,493,24}Kakurai\NKayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.82,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Her smile is remarkably cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:11.07,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Her popularity alone has exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:16.58,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,At the Haido City handshake event, there was a \Nhuge line in front of only Kakurai Kayoko's booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:21.56,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently, the other \Nmembers thought poorly of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:26.59,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,On one occasion, they became jealous \Nof the amount of gifts she received.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.10,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,On another occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:44.39,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,they all ignored Kakurai Kayoko when \Nshe showed up late to a dance lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.90,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,On yet another occasion, \Nin the powder room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:08.33,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Due to that string of incidents, the \Nsmile finally disappeared from her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:20.22,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,She was taken away in an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:27.99,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,That night, the blonde in sunglasses dine \Nand dashed at a ramen restaurant in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.71,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get it at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:35.07,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,but after what the Beika City family \Nrestaurant waitstaff said today...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.68,DCItalic,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,The smile of the blonde in \Nsunglasses who dine and dashed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.71,DCItalic,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,looked just like Kakurai Kayoko's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.29,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it clicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:48.73,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,The blonde in sunglasses who dine and dashed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.84,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,at a Haido City ramen restaurant three months ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.59,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,may have been Kakurai Kayoko as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:09:02.60,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,After suffering the jealousy of the other \NDDPP members, Kakurai Kayoko was distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:10.02,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,She awoke in a hospital room and felt hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:14.03,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,She looked around the room \Nand saw her bag there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:20.53,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Inside her bag were the blonde wig \Nand sunglasses she wore onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:25.82,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Disguising herself using those, \Nshe left the hospital room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.04,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,wandered around the city at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:37.95,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually dine and dashed \Nat a ramen restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.59,sign_8500_65_Sasai_New_Haido_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1902,596)}New Haido Ramen\N\NSasai
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:46.18,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs26\c&H26272C&\3c&HF1F1F1&\shad0\b1\bord3}The Truth Behind \NKakurai Kayoko's Hiatus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:43.55,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, Kakurai Kayoko is taking a \Nbreak from the entertainment industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.90,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,She's recuperating at a \Nhospital in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:53.28,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Did the distraught and recuperating Kakurai \NKayoko leave the hospital in the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.61,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,disguise herself as the blonde in sunglasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:59.94,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,and dine and dash at a Beika\NCity family restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:06.20,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Great Detective Mori Kogoro,\NI'd like to ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.21,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Please crack this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.32,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:21.60,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,He's already asleep and solvingâ€”no, \Nmasterfully cracking the case while he naps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.18,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:30.69,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He's just asleep because \Nhe drank too many beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.94,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.60,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.74,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, at Beika Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.95,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.20,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently cracking a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.76,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Cracking a case?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.94,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm cracking a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.45,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I asked for his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.21,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yamasato from the Beika \NCity 4-chome police box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.72,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Mori's daughter Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.01,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What case are you solving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Ran, weren't \Nyou about to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.97,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I just saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:10.44,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Saw who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.19,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.11,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.02,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.54,sign_16437_142_Mori_Detective_A,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(312,45,312,85)\frz14.66\c&H8DAA95&\3c&H6A785E&\blur1}Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.54,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Kakurai Kayoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:31.71,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where did you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.04,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Where? At Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.14,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.80,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,On my way home from school just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.70,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I was walking through Beika \NPark with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:48.56,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like there was an on-location \Nshoot for a drama or movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:51.56,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to see who was appearing in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.06,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,so we searched the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:12:00.77,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's when we found a woman \Nwho looked like an attendant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.57,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,standing in front of a van.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:07.83,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,We were certain someone famous was inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:14.45,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,We snuck behind the van without \Nbeing seen by her and looked inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:16.84,DCItalic,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:20.76,DCItalic,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.22,DCItalic,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.26,DCItalic,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:47.16,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I think they were filming \NKakurai Kayoko-chan's first movie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:51.36,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,after returning from her hiatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:54.34,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,How old was Kakurai Kayoko's female manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.04,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.63,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Around 40?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.87,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,How old was her female attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.05,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,The woman's age?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.65,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Around 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.40,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,That's about the same age as Kakurai Kayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:12.31,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I've got something to \Ndo, so I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:19.82,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the thing I personally \Nfeared the most has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:26.77,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,The distraught and recuperating Kakurai Kayoko \Nshould've retired from the entertainment industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.59,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,But her agencyâ€”no,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:33.62,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,the entertainment industry is \Ntrying to force Kakurai Kayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.33,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,to return when she hasn't recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.33,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Mori Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.06,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm about to tell you \Nare my personal thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.24,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly not any \Nkind of logical deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.05,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:54.12,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko came to Beika City in order \Nto film her first movie after her return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:59.60,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,However, her mental health \Nhad not yet recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.18,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to withstand the pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:15.62,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,she disguised herself as the blonde in \Nsunglasses, left the shooting location,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:21.38,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,and headed to a family restaurant where she \Ndine and dashed on a chocolate parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:24.64,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Later, in order to hide the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.66,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,her female manager and attendant \Ndisguised themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:31.69,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,as a mother and daughter \Nand went to pay her bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:37.14,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,That's just me clumsily thinking aloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.50,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be delighted if you were \Nable to use it for future reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:44.65,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Detective Mori Kogoro! \NCrack the case, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.11,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to deduce after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.41,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Crack the case, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:55.68,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Does this guy just want to show off his \Ndetective skills to a famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.84,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Crack the case, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.41,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.31,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Crack the case, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:04.67,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Does this case really need a \Ndetective to crack it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.67,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I shall crack this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.84,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank youâ€”ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:13.51,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my head on your shoes. Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.90,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan, get in touch with Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.67,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What was up with that police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.66,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:39.20,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran, where did Kakurai Kayoko's tears \Nfall when you saw her inside the car
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.58,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,at the filming location in Beika Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.80,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Where were they falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:53.01,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,On the red shoes she was wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of shoes was her attendant wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:58.26,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Her attendant's shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.77,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,They were sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:06.21,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Officer Yamasato, where did the \Ncrying daughter's tears fall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:10.03,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,while being held by her \Nmother at the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:14.53,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If they fell on sneakers, then the \Ndaughter was actually the attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If they fell on red shoes, \Nthen it's possible that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.64,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.34,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Red shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:28.82,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:30.66,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.56,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:39.31,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Kakurai Kayoko herself \Nwho went to pay the bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.00,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is stranger than fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.59,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit odd for me to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:47.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,but allow to me admit that even I, \Nthe great detective Mori Kogoro,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.87,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I can hang up now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:50.04,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}am a bit surprised by this conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The mother and daughter who went \Nto the Beika City restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,to apologize were the manager \Nand Kakurai Kayoko herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:02.41,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Kakurai \NKayoko isn't distraught?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.04,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko is not distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:09.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Three months ago, on the day of the \NHaido City ramen restaurant incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:13.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,after suffering the jealousy \Nof the other DDPP members
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:16.51,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and being taken to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.14,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,as you deduced, Kakurai \NKayoko woke up hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:25.48,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,took the disguise in her bag \Nand left the hospital room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:30.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what the manager disguised \Nas her mother and older sister said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:34.34,DCItalic,MOTHER,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter forgot her wallet and panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.66,DCItalic,SISTER,0000,0000,0000,,My sister forgot her wallet and panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.70,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.70,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,She really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.96,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,...forget her wallet and panic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:59.14,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Kakurai \NKayoko is just an airhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.18,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.97,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(613,1)\b1\fs32\pos(324,18)\fnTimes New Roman\bord3\shad0\c&H000000&\3c&HF7EEEA&\blur1}Air Head
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.13,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.10,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.86,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,An airhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:16.11,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,My Kakurai Kayoko isn't an airhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:19.80,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My Kakurai Kayoko isn't an airhead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.96,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Officer Yamasato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.32,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}my Kakurai Kayoko isn't an airhead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.26,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}my Kakurai Kayoko isn't an airhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.87,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I need a drink, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.37,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You're on duty, Officer Yamasato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:39.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Officer Yamasato, what's wrong with \Nyour Kakurai Kayoko being an airhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.93,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Officer Yamasato, you underestimate idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.39,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,I've underestimated idols?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:50.24,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Going forward, idols must be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.33,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:57.65,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps what Ran saw wasn't \Nher practicing her smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.53,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,but practicing how not to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.96,DCItalic,MANAGER,0000,0000,0000,,No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.54,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:13.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko is trying \Nto become a new person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:16.52,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,A new Kakurai Kayoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:19.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Your Kakurai Kayoko is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:23.75,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She has the strength to withstand the \Njealousy of the other DDPP members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:29.43,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And above all, Kakurai \NKayoko has acting skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.14,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko's acting skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.44,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.03,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakurai Kayoko has a cute smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.44,sign_28195_276_Kakurai_Kayoko,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(434,-76,434,56)\frz348.3\3c&HACB6C9&}Kakurai Kayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.44,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,That's all she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.32,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:45.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the female manager appear to be her \Nmother at the Beika City family restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:48.58,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she appear to be her older sister \Nat the Haido City ramen restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.21,DCMain,YAMASATO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:52.67,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what the waitstaff said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:56.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who dine and dashed \Nand the girl accompanied
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.27,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,by her mother seemed like \Ntwo different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:02.34,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That was because of Kakurai Kayoko's acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She played a daughter at the \NBeika City family restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.47,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and a younger sister at the \NHaido City ramen restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.36,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this if not acting skills?
